  "title": "Easy Bee",
  "description": "A completly new way to trasport bees with extra tweaks",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/1154134.svg\" alt=\"title\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-lime?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fneoforged.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">A completly new way to trasport bees with extra tweaks</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>All current features:</strong></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">- <strong>Bee</strong> (Item-like)</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Inspired from <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/easy-villagers\">EasyVillager</a> (mod) , this item allow you to store and place on later anywhere a bee without need to lure with flowers!</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">- <strong>Scoop</strong> (aka bee net)</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">A tool that allow you to convert Bees (Entity) to Item form</span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Easy%20Bee/new.gif?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"927\" height=\"810\" /></div>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">-&nbsp;<strong>Floreal Fertilizer</strong></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">A special bonemeal that only generate all small flowers&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Easy%20Bee/floreal.gif?raw=true\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">and more on future</span></div>\n\n&nbsp;\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This mod was originally a custom feature of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/ironberry-expert\">Ironberry Expert (Modpack)</a>&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Now completly a&nbsp;<strong>standalone mod</strong></span></div>\n\n&nbsp;\n<details>\n<summary>Original Gif from Ironberry</summary>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Easy%20Bee/old.gif?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"751\" /></p>\n</details>\n",
